title: General comments
description: Any general comments the coder wants to add about this study

title: Country
description: Country (or countries) where the data were collected

title: Device
description: Device type for which the application was developed, e.g. 'smartwatch', 'vr', 'smartphone', etc

title: Platform
description: The platform, e.g. android, windows, etc

title: Target groups
description: Description of the target group(s) of the intervention

title: Target group specification
description: Specification of the defining characteristics of this target group (e.g. a health issue, (sub-)culture, region, gender, etc)

title: Methods
description: Description of the methods used by the study

title: Evaluaton
description: Whether this article describes the results of an evaluation (including effect size estimates) or not.

title: Sample size
description: Total number of human participants in the study (note: the actual sample size may be larger if multiple observations are collected per participant)
